This hook allows the display of up to ten extra "/ link" tags for taskforces. It is commonly used with {{tlx|WPBannerMeta/hooks/taskforces}}. It should be attached to the {{para|HOOK_NESTED}} hook. The parameters and their definitions are the same as in the standard implementation: see the [[Template:WPBannerMeta#Taskforces|documentation]] for more details.
