   |pd|  |nl|  |  |  |  |  |=
   |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |=
   |bl|  |  |  |pd|  |  |qd|=
   |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |=
   |pl|pl|pl|  |  |pl|pl|bd|=
   |rl|nl|bl|ql|  |  |  |kl|=
||
}}
=Ruy Lopez, Riga Variation, Main Line=

Black takes the rook with the pawn, correctly. Now white's next move is forced: [[/12. Qd8+|12. Qd8+]]. This is the only move white has that will divert the black queen from the attack. Note that [[/12. Qd8+/12...Qxd8|12...Qxd8]] is literally black's only legal move. White follows up thereafter with 13. Nxd8.

{{ChessMid}}
