=Ruy Lopez, Riga Variation, Main Line=

White's next move [[/13. Nxd8+|13. Nxd8+]] is likewise forced, completing the queen trade. There is a discovered check coming from the bishop, but nevertheless, white's knight will be hanging and black should take it next turn.

{{ChessMid}}
