[[pl:Sidux_-_czyli_Debian_sid_krok_po_kroku_dla_każdego/Programy_użytkowe/Wyszukiwanie_plików]] == Catfish == : Having problems with finding any file, folder or application use Catfish. :1. Installation: apt-get install catfish :2. Run the application: Menu-> Accessories-> Catfish :3. Type a file name in search field on left top side. :4. As additional option choose for example: ::a. exact match. ::b. hidden files. ::c. limit results. ::d. file type: document, image, music, video. ::e. searching folder. :5. The application will find any file matching with key word and will display it's size and location as well. [[File:Catfish1en.png|center|600px]]
