=== Usage ===
Place this template on a user's talk page to let them know a book they contributed to was deleted. To say what book was deleted use {{para|page}}. You can provide a custom explanation with {{para|reason}}. You can provide an optional signature with {{para|sig}}.

=== Examples ===
{{tlxs|deleted|page&#61;Page}}
{{deleted|page=Page}}
{{tlxs|deleted|page&#61;Page|reason&#61;spam|sig&#61;yes}}
{{deleted|page=Page|reason=spam|sig=yes}}

